like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"622912c3de765808289a796ad97440ca5f467930","tid":1917103,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"究竟仲有邊個牌子安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"只要係人造，就唔會完美"},{"pid":"bb7c8173dd15f30fcf665e4df39d2940eef688c7","tid":1917103,"uid":121058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"AMD蘇大媽係共諜<br />\n專登留個後門比共產黨中出 然後又低價搶市佔率<br />\n同華為既做法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5347c43c565999640758c56c792392e229f5e952","tid":1917103,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:52:11.000Z","msg":"唯有等zen3出就換新機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958b33ec4ccd11d3d840e9ebaa58900517d20d31","tid":1917103,"uid":236750,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2bcf4bd509e94ee80ca8cb7629196933e198e04a","tid":1917103,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"自 2018 年 Intel 的處理器安全漏洞相繼曝光，嚴重程度及影響範圍不一，其中最讓 Intel 焦頭爛額的應該就是 Spectre 及 Meltdown 漏洞，在發現不久之後 AMD 已表明 Zen 2 產品將從底層對 Spectre 類型的漏洞完全免疫，不過有研究人員最新發現了一種新的測通道攻擊方式，隸屬大名鼎鼎的&ldquo;Spectre&rdquo;系列，而今次「中招」的處理器是 AMD 由 2011 年至 2019 年推出的所有處理器，如 Bulldozer 家族及最新的 Zen 家族等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/09143017171605743488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F09143017171605743488.jpg&h=edd2f486&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n奧地利格拉茨技術大學的研究人員發佈論文稱，發現了兩種隸屬於 Spectre 系列的新側通道攻擊方式「Collide+Probe」及「Load+Reload」，統稱為&ldquo;Take A Way&rdquo;，兩者都利用了 AMD L1D Cache 緩存方式預測器的弱點，該工具可預測數據在處理器中的儲存位置，以檢測何時訪問該數據洩漏記憶體資料內容。在通過將新發現的漏洞再與現有的方法相結合，研究人員竟然成功在實驗室本地測試及雲端伺服器中破解 AMD 處理器並取得用家的機密資料及竊取加密數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/0915080989205066853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F0915080989205066853.jpg&h=0d9029a3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n具體來說，研究人員共測試了 15 款不同型號的 AMD 處理器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其中早期使用舊架構的不存在&ldquo;Take A Way&rdquo;的漏洞，例如 K8 架構的 Athlon 64 X2 3800、Turion II Neo N40L 等。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/0914302121324276460.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F0914302121324276460.jpg&h=70b565a3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n不過一些新架構處理器全部淪陷了，包括 Bulldozer 架構的 FX-4100、Piledriver 架構的 FX-8350、Steamroller 架構的 A10-7870K、Zen 架構的 Threadripper 1920X/1950X/1700X、Zen+ 架構的 Threadripper 2970WX、Zen 2 架構的 Ryzen 7 3700X <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />及 EPYC 7401P/7571，其中兩顆 EPYC 處理器在雲端進行測試，其他處理器是在實驗室本地測試的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19063/10_年內由_Bulldozer_至_Zen_2_全中招_AMD_處理器被發現Takeaway安全漏洞\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19063%2F10_%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E7%94%B1_Bulldozer_%E8%87%B3_Zen_2_%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B_AMD_%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E8%A2%AB%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BETakeaway%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=d210495b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19063/10_年內由_Bulldozer_至_Zen_2_全中招_AMD_處理器被發現Takeaway安全漏洞</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:01:35.000Z","msg":"而今次有發現 AMD 處理器「Take A Way」漏洞的奧地利格拉茨技術大學，則被爆出相關的漏洞研究是由 Intel 發起，主要研究及追查自家與其他競爭產品存在的漏洞，並進行全面的資安檢測，所以是否 CPU 製造商鬥爭的「陰謀論」，各位就要自己去分析了!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6532857b92920027a8b8a0137847b9e5a3ff3de7","tid":1917103,"uid":87437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9bc55b6ea8270b2d80c9bfbb38fb9715821b25b","tid":1917103,"uid":81723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4890fd4e3cf3d946b0666bebc1b157a7eb307d9e","tid":1917103,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"AMD 官方表示<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目前不會發佈更新</span></strong></span>，建議用戶<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><em>確保操作系統是最新版本及裝上防毒軟件</em></span></span>，並定時下載最新版本的韌體更新，就可以將受影響的程度降至最低。<br />\n<br />\nWindows Update = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:16:04.000Z","msg":"咁你掉左粒amd未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"Zen2唔要就俾我，反而點都好過Intel"},{"pid":"0c9585b35684e02b23330098fd953aad6c2e7849","tid":1917103,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"958b33ec4ccd11d3d840e9ebaa58900517d20d31","tid":1917103,"uid":236750,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2bcf4bd509e94ee80ca8cb7629196933e198e04a","tid":1917103,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"自 2018 年 Intel 的處理器安全漏洞相繼曝光，嚴重程度及影響範圍不一，其中最讓 Intel 焦頭爛額的應該就是 Spectre 及 Meltdown 漏洞，在發現不久之後 AMD 已表明 Zen 2 產品將從底層對 Spectre 類型的漏洞完全免疫，不過有研究人員最新發現了一種新的測通道攻擊方式，隸屬大名鼎鼎的&ldquo;Spectre&rdquo;系列，而今次「中招」的處理器是 AMD 由 2011 年至 2019 年推出的所有處理器，如 Bulldozer 家族及最新的 Zen 家族等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/09143017171605743488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F09143017171605743488.jpg&h=edd2f486&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n奧地利格拉茨技術大學的研究人員發佈論文稱，發現了兩種隸屬於 Spectre 系列的新側通道攻擊方式「Collide+Probe」及「Load+Reload」，統稱為&ldquo;Take A Way&rdquo;，兩者都利用了 AMD L1D Cache 緩存方式預測器的弱點，該工具可預測數據在處理器中的儲存位置，以檢測何時訪問該數據洩漏記憶體資料內容。在通過將新發現的漏洞再與現有的方法相結合，研究人員竟然成功在實驗室本地測試及雲端伺服器中破解 AMD 處理器並取得用家的機密資料及竊取加密數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/0915080989205066853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F0915080989205066853.jpg&h=0d9029a3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n具體來說，研究人員共測試了 15 款不同型號的 AMD 處理器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其中早期使用舊架構的不存在&ldquo;Take A Way&rdquo;的漏洞，例如 K8 架構的 Athlon 64 X2 3800、Turion II Neo N40L 等。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/0914302121324276460.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F0914302121324276460.jpg&h=70b565a3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n不過一些新架構處理器全部淪陷了，包括 Bulldozer 架構的 FX-4100、Piledriver 架構的 FX-8350、Steamroller 架構的 A10-7870K、Zen 架構的 Threadripper 1920X/1950X/1700X、Zen+ 架構的 Threadripper 2970WX、Zen 2 架構的 Ryzen 7 3700X <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />及 EPYC 7401P/7571，其中兩顆 EPYC 處理器在雲端進行測試，其他處理器是在實驗室本地測試的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19063/10_年內由_Bulldozer_至_Zen_2_全中招_AMD_處理器被發現Takeaway安全漏洞\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19063%2F10_%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E7%94%B1_Bulldozer_%E8%87%B3_Zen_2_%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B_AMD_%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E8%A2%AB%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BETakeaway%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=d210495b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19063/10_年內由_Bulldozer_至_Zen_2_全中招_AMD_處理器被發現Takeaway安全漏洞</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:01:35.000Z","msg":"而今次有發現 AMD 處理器「Take A Way」漏洞的奧地利格拉茨技術大學，則被爆出相關的漏洞研究是由 Intel 發起，主要研究及追查自家與其他競爭產品存在的漏洞，並進行全面的資安檢測，所以是否 CPU 製造商鬥爭的「陰謀論」，各位就要自己去分析了!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"唧牙膏仲唔夠<br />\n仲要出陰招"},{"pid":"d0592972a0f2237eb731070e8a9a24ed411e2d06","tid":1917103,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:14:32.000Z","msg":"股價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5857526f5b4bf90eef280950da9e9d7d6cbf2f81","tid":1917103,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T18:07:35.000Z","msg":"zen3 amd YES<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f320bb7b0df7010b687665c92642b5571473008","tid":1917103,"uid":60100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47001ea683976fc3fe877101d7a216aa56f7317f","tid":1917103,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:54:09.000Z","msg":"就「Take A Way」漏洞，AMD 官方已作出回應：&ldquo;我們已經知曉一篇新的論文稱 AMD 處理器存在潛在的安全漏洞，可利用惡意代碼和緩存相關特性，以非正常方式發送用戶數據。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/09143018181525686486.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F09143018181525686486.jpg&h=5a3d0fd8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n <br />\nAMD 認為，「Take A Way」漏洞並非新型預測攻擊，只是研究人員將此數據路徑與預測執行測通道漏洞聯繫在一起。因此 AMD 官方表示目前不會發佈更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，建議用戶確保操作系統是最新版本及裝上防毒軟件，並定時下載最新版本的韌體更新，就可以將受影響的程度降至最低。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:53:47.000Z","msg":"AMD即係話 <br />\n你搞錯左 你拎條水喉 就話佢係蛇<br />\n搞錯左wor<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過amd就無講條水喉係咪真係漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f7fcff38ab4df9ac017724a8943caa81f506a2","tid":1917103,"uid":180362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"AMD唔更新係好事<br />\n以AMD既能力，更新完會更多bugs"},{"pid":"33c4eac95872505a43b350b384f105d2393e95ea","tid":1917103,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4295be4f5ddd3b1c8b66bf4678801943483d2b52","tid":1917103,"uid":43274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f7fcff38ab4df9ac017724a8943caa81f506a2","tid":1917103,"uid":180362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"AMD唔更新係好事<br />\n以AMD既能力，更新完會更多bugs"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"更唔更都多bugs架啦<br />\n唔更新咪又繼續多bugs"}]}